        "Baseline: fully serverless-no-VPC — no always-on NAT, ALB, or instance; ~$0 idle floor",
        "SQS standard queue decouples checkout ingest from fulfillment; DLQ + redrive after 3 failures",
        "DynamoDB on-demand absorbs checkout write spikes without pre-provisioning",
        "Lambda reserved concurrency (checkout=100, fulfillment=50) controls burst drain rate",
        "Fulfillment idempotency: conditional UpdateItem on orderId prevents double-fulfillment on redelivery",
        "Outbox pattern: PENDING written at checkout, FULFILLED written at fulfillment, SES delivery event flips record — observable and retryable",
        "CloudWatch alarms on error rate, latency, DLQ depth → SNS → email on-call notification"
      ],
      "tradeoffs": [
