      "delta": [
        "Active-active multi-region: Route 53 latency routing + health checks across two CloudFront + API Gateway + Lambda stacks",
        "DynamoDB Global Tables: multi-region replication replaces single-region on-demand table",
        "SQS standard → FIFO: ordered fulfillment with dedup ID; prevents out-of-order double-fulfillment across regions",
        "EventBridge replaces SNS fan-out: archive + replay capability for event replay after outage; rules decouple consumers",
        "Lambda provisioned concurrency (checkout=50, fulfill=25): eliminates cold-start latency tail under burst",
        "CloudWatch anomaly detection + SLO error-budget alarms added alongside threshold alarms",
        "PagerDuty escalation endpoint added to ops_sns for P1 incidents; Slack remains for warnings",
        "Shield Advanced on both CloudFront distributions for DDoS response + cost protection"
      ],
      "tradeoffs": [
        "Global Tables + FIFO SQS + EventBridge + provisioned concurrency significantly increase cost vs balanced",
        "Active-active multi-region adds operational complexity (conflict resolution policy on Global Tables must be defined)",
        "EventBridge has slightly higher latency than direct SNS for fan-out; justified by archive/replay for DR",
        "Provisioned concurrency wastes capacity during off-peak; consider scheduled scaling for predictable traffic patterns"
      ],
